name: Paper Plane Adventures Games - The Living Room Act 2 Game
name_original: Paper Plane Adventures Games - The Living Room Act 2 Game
description:
Fly through the living room as your favorite paper airplane in part two of the paper airplane saga. Avoid incoming origami animals as you collect coins to unlock new great paper airplanes!
New power ups, new plane, and two new living rooms to play! Now you can fly paper airplanes in the living room without getting into trouble!
Games only available on Apple Devises.
